&lt;li&gt;Partner with customers to align Triple Whale solutions with their evolving needs and business priorities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead commercial conversations, presentations, and negotiations with decision-makers across customer organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create scalable plays and workflows that leverage account signals, usage trends, and customer behavior to drive expansion opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor account performance, product adoption, utilization trends, and customer sentiment to uncover opportunities and mitigate risk.&lt;/li&gt;
