&lt;p&gt;The right person brings strong modeling depth, sharp product judgment, and the business context to work in ambiguity. Fintech, lending, credit, or risk experience is strongly preferred — but we&#39;re also open to senior data scientists from adjacent domains who&#39;ve built high-stakes models in complex, data-rich environments.&lt;/p&gt;
