&lt;p&gt;Triple Whale sits at the center of a merchant&#39;s growth stack. Our product is only as strong as the data we can reliably ingest, normalize, enrich, and activate across commerce platforms, ad networks, pixels, server-side events, warehouses, and partner tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As APIs change, privacy rules tighten, and merchants expect near real-time data they can trust, integrations become a core product surface, not just plumbing. We need someone who can turn messy third-party APIs into dependable customer experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll work with our technical integrations team end-to-end: which platforms we integrate with, how we design durable data contracts, how customers authenticate and connect accounts, how we monitor freshness and failures, and how we launch, maintain, and communicate integrations at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
